import React, { useState } from 'react'

 const Search = () => {
     const [text, setText] = useState
    return (
        <section className='search'>
            <form>
                <input 
                type='text'
                className='form-control'
                placeholder='Search characters'
                autoFocus
            />
            </form>
        </section>
       
    )
}

export default Search
